issue.title: Is there any document about `ext.flutter.name` or `ext.flutter.inspector.name`?

labels.name: vm-service
labels.description: The VM Service Protocol, both the specification and its implementation

issue.body:
Hi, I'm looking into this document to make my Flutter inspector and vm client.
https://github.com/dart-lang/sdk/blob/main/runtime/vm/service/service.md#private-rpcs-types-and-properties

It's well-organized document about public RPCs like `getVM` (thank you!) but I couldn't find `ext.flutter.name` or `ext.flutter.inspector.name` methods although they look no private method.
I have looked into Flutter repository but I only found https://github.com/flutter/flutter/blob/7c860ddf970575d4ca6dd0ccc4bd823613a16359/packages/flutter/lib/src/widgets/widget_inspector.dart#L843

If I missed anything, I'm sorry but do you have any public document about them? and If no, why?
